  "source_notes": "Originally this entry had the last name \"Caymmy\": Marcello Borges quotes a biography written by Stella Caymmy, one of his granddaughters.\\n\\nOn 21/10/14 Sy Scholfield changed the last name to \"Caymmi,\" quoting from from the same biography: \"Dorival Caymmi: o mar e o tempo\" by Stella Caymmi (Editora 34, 2001), p. 34: \"Quando Deraldo Caymmi nasceu, em 5 de novembro de 1912, o casal já tinha alugado uma casinha na rua do Bângala, 77 — hoje rua Luiz Gama — , onde também nasceu o quarto filho do casal, Dorival Caymmi, em 30 de abril de 1914, às 22h50.\"\\n\\nTranslation: When Deraldo Caymmi was born on 5 November 1912, the couple had rented a small house at 77 Bangala Street - today Luiz Gama street - where the fourth child, Dorival Caymmi, was also born, on 30 April 1914 at 22:50. \\n",
